      """
      cookbook 'fake'
      """
    And I write to "Berksfile.lock" with:
      """
      DEPENDENCIES
        non-existent (~> 0.1)
          path: /this/path/does/not/exist
      """
    When I successfully run `berks install`
    And the file "Berksfile.lock" should contain:
      """
